They bind the battle with a vlogger who might be involved in a double kill. They also experience the dangers of online dating and are faced with corruption within Justice. Samantha is again waiting for all the businesses. She is currently working on internal affairs and does not leave unused opportunities this season to make the team members sick. Finally, someone who seems to keep an eye on Fenna and leaves strange letters for her. Who is this stalker?

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: On Fenna Kremers's first day as a detective in Leeuwarden, an offender escapes. It seems that this man would like revenge and there threatening to fall some victims if he don't found fast enough. Fenna's idiosyncratic way of working is not by all her new colleagues in the taste.

episodes.name: Rebecca
episodes.overview: During the Sneekweek there arrives a threatening letter at the headquarters. If certain requirements are not satisfied, there will be for the thousands visitors a deadly consequences. The team does everything to identify the sender of the letter and prevent an attack committed in Sneek.

episodes.name: Vuurduin
episodes.overview: Bram and Fenna travel to Vlieland when there's a body of a young man wash ashore. At first they suspected that the victim was beaten overboard. But then they discover that the boy had a reason to visit Vlieland. He was looking for something and he wasn't the only one.

episodes.name: Testfase
episodes.overview: During a burglary at a secondary school a locker is stolen, containing the national examinations that are about to begin. If the investigation team don't found the locker enough, there will be implications for thousands of high school students. Because of time pressure, tensions within the investigation team are high.

episodes.name: Één voor allen
episodes.overview: The brothers Carlo and Olivier were held responsible for numerous violent crimes in Friesland for years. Until one day they disappeared and nobody heard anything from them. It seems that the brothers are back, when there find a violent raid takes place in a restaurant. And they came back for a special reason.

episodes.name: Teruggefloten
episodes.overview: In Leeuwarden there's a wooden box found with a amputated man's hand. Short after this there is found a second box with another part of a man's body. The detective team does everything what's possible to prevent even more boxes. But who is the perpetrator and what does he wants?

episodes.name: Hartpijn
episodes.overview: A boy and girl of seventeen are not returned from sailing at the IJsselmeer. The task for Fenna and Evert to immediate their family on the height. If the girl fished later that day she is still alive and well, meanwhile Fenna has discovered that there are strange things going on within her family.

episodes.name: Vermoorde onschuld
episodes.overview: In the Thialf Stadium is a charity hockey game between two teams but it is overshadowed by the murder of two boys from the youth selection. The offender is already arrested, but Fenna has serious doubts whether this man actually did it. Then there arrives someone from the past and again there lives at stakes.

episodes.name: Een oud bekende
episodes.overview: A dangerous criminal knows to escape during a transfer to Leeuwarden. If it appears that this man played a role in the history of Fenna and he now may be on its coined. The pressure to find this man grows. Through all this, Fenna confronted with memories she rather forget.

episodes.name: Alles op zijn tijd
episodes.overview: Fenna is in bad shape. She sits at home and it seems no one to contact her. As one of the other detectives announce to leave, Carla sees her team slowly disintegrate. Then Leeuwarden startled by a winding-reaching consequences.

The team puts everything on everything to find out where these pills come from. Meanwhile Menno takes an important decision in his life that will keep him chasing for a long time.

episodes.name: Stille wateren, diepe gronden
episodes.overview: On a construction site a coffin is found during excavation work involving the body of a woman who has been missing for years. All traces indicate that they are buried alive. Then several boxes are excavated in the same area. Fenna and her team find out that a serial killer buried his victims alive, who has dumped for years. Then, Commissioner Vreeswijk suddenly disappears. Has she become the victim of this ruthless killer? And can she still be saved?

Then there will be a very strange movie on the internet. The young woman is pictured with a strap around her neck. And next to her is a counter. If the counter is 0, then it is suspended

To bring this situation to a good end, Fenna Kremer has to make a decision that will fully affect her feel and will pursue her for a long time.

episodes.overview: The team finds a corpse, but they can not track the cause of death. Both Liselotte and a paratrooper face a riddle. However, it does not stay with this one body; The team is struggling to pick up the killer who looks smarter than the team together. The team sees no other reason to lure the perpetrator with bait.

episodes.name: Kind van de rekening
episodes.overview: A six year old boy walks away from home and his parents do not know what's going on. A search does not matter and the longer the boy is missing, the more worry the police make. The next morning the boy's teddy bear is found at the house of a convicted person

episodes.name: De bekentenis
episodes.overview: Justice Officer Jelle van Santen gets a visit to an intruder late in the evening. The intruder flees when Jelle's daughter is unexpectedly downstairs. It seems to be a failed robbery and Jelle tries to argue that too. However, Carla does not trust it all and feels that Jelle has something for her.
